                  Sample Case Description
                </Typography>
                <Typography variant="body2" color="textSecondary">
                  • Case Type<br/>
                  • Who are you?<br/>
                  &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Petitioner/Applicant/Respondent<br/>
